Doctor Michael Kaufmann,[p]
He definitely has some secret.[p]
While I am not sure whether it is connected to me rescuing Cheryl or not, [p]
he knows the main reason why this town has undergone a transformation.[p]
I followed him so that he did not notice me.[p]


[tb_hide_message_window  ]
[playse  loop="true"  storage="04_-_Fog_Noiz.ogg"  ]
