Inside, ancient dust is everywhere, and the room reeks of mildew.[p]
It looks to be a garage.[p]
Oil, a sprayer, tires, and such, have been placed on a dirty metal shelf.[p]
"Odd..."[p]
Kaufmann is nowhere to be found. [p]
There is only one other door in the room, and it is slightly open.[p]
He must have went through there into another room.[p]
However, I did not go after him right away. [p]
Instead, my attention turned to the motorcycle near the wall and I stopped.[p]


[tb_hide_message_window  ]
[playse  storage="CHAN.mp3"  ]
