The gas tank of the motorcycle differs from the rest of motorcycle, as it is oddly clean and shiny.[p]
The motorcycle is so covered in dust, that it is not possible to even distinguish what color it is.[p]
But I get the feeling that the gas tank area alone has been fiddled with by someone.[p]
I try gently opening the gas tank.[p]


[tb_hide_message_window  ]
[playse  storage="BIKE_GASTANK_SOUND.ogg"  ]
