Inside the gas tank, there is a black vinyl bag that is protecting a small glass bottle. [p]
At the moment I was about to reach out to it, a familiar voice stopped me.[p]


[tb_hide_message_window  ]
[playbgm  loop="true"  storage="03_-_Air_In_The_Mind.ogg"  ]
[bg  time="500"  method="crossfade"  storage="harry_12-3.gif"  ]
