"Give me that!"[p]
When I turned, Kaufmann was just glaring at me, his face white with anger. [p]
His clenched fists are shaking with rage.[p]
"What is this?"[p]
"That's none of your business![p]
Instead of messing with that, how about coming up with a way to get out of here?"[p]
"Humph."[p]
"You shouldn't be hanging around here goofing off![p]
What do you think you are doing?[p]
You want to get yourself killed!?[p]
Get outta here!"[p]
Even if he had not said that I understood.[p]
I didn't know just how important this small bottle was to him, but I didn't think that it would help me to find Cheryl.[p]
So I gave it to him.[p]
"Okay, take it easy."[p]
"Unless you want to die, keep your mind on business. [p]
Got it?"[p]


