I think, "That guy's got to be involved with the local drug racket.[p]
Man, was he pissed.[p]
And in such a rush, too. [p]
That was probably dope in the bottle.[p]
Anyway, better let him do as he pleases.[p]
There's more than my life at stake."[p]
I then realize, that I am wasting time, and immediately leave the hotel.[p]


